{"word":"G5294 - ὑποτίθημι - hypotíthēmi - hoop-ot-ith'-ay-mee - Lay down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποτίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypotíthēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ot-ith'-ay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lay down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உபதேசி"},{"paragraph":"to place under"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>place underneath</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>hazard</i>, (reflexively) to <i>suggest:</i> - lay down, put in remembrance.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}